  "detailed_description": "Slime Alchemist combines roguelike deckbuilding and turn-based tactics with open-ended exploration, dynamic turn order, and enemy card crafting to create a unique strategic mix.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Set the pace of battle.</strong> The cards you play determine when enemies will act. Choose your cards wisely to unleash powerful combos on your foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567800/extras/e247a6d17b435b34e8d5d1e37b3d038f.poster.avif?t=1703269909\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567800/extras/e247a6d17b435b34e8d5d1e37b3d038f.webm?t=1703269909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567800/extras/e247a6d17b435b34e8d5d1e37b3d038f.mp4?t=1703269909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong> Explore a procedurally generated world.</strong> Explore freely to refine your deck and gain powerful passives; but tread carefully, as each step makes your enemies stronger. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567800/extras/b90ea4f5699ea435ad1628631038ea61.poster.avif?t=1703269909\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567800/extras/b90ea4f5699ea435ad1628631038ea61.webm?t=1703269909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567800/extras/b90ea4f5699ea435ad1628631038ea61.mp4?t=1703269909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong> Build your deck from the techniques of vanquished foes.</strong> Every enemy drops its unique deck of cards on death; combine and sacrifice them to create your own hybrid fighting style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567800/extras/93dfad1a7982186de73b158d6f46b62e.poster.avif?t=1703269909\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567800/extras/93dfad1a7982186de73b158d6f46b62e.webm?t=1703269909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567800/extras/93dfad1a7982186de73b158d6f46b62e.mp4?t=1703269909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
